Theodore Newton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore_Newton_(actor) 0 Theodore Newton (August 4, 1904 - February 28, 1963) was an American movie, stage and old-time radio actor. He was sometimes billed as Ted Newton. He was born in Lawrenceville, New Jersey. He died of cancer in Hollywood, California, age 58.
